Boilermake-cuda - An extension for Boilermake with CUDA support.
Forked from Boilermake - A reusable, but flexible, boilerplate makefile.


Overview
--------
Boilermake-cuda is an extension for Boilermake with CUDA support.
For compiling CUDA files NVCC compiler and NVIDIA drivers are required.

This project is fork from Boilermake: A reusable, but flexible, boilerplate
makefile. For more details see: 

Boilermake-cuda is free software. It is released under the GNU General Public
License.


